data.description: Indulge in the ultimate relaxation haven with this exquisite home! Step into luxury with a meticulously upgraded residence boasting custom paint, porcelain tile flooring on the first level, and stunning granite countertops, complemented by stainless steel appliances. Washer, dryer, and refrigerator in both the kitchen and garage stay with the home. Bask in the warmth of natural light streaming through the strategically added window in the family room, creating a cozy and inviting atmosphere. The primary retreat is a spacious sanctuary, offering ample room for a sitting or office area. With a generous size, this retreat becomes a private oasis within your own home. Don't miss the chance to experience the comfort and elegance of this residence – schedule your appointment today and make this dream home yours!
